VOID ID(main) LPAREN RPAREN
LBRACE
DOUBLE ID(r) COMMA ID(pi) SEMICOLON
ID(pi) ASSIGN CT_REAL(3.140000) SEMICOLON
ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("r=") RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(r) ASSIGN ID(get_d) LPAREN RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("perimeter=") RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(put_d) LPAREN CT_INT(2) ID(e0) MUL ID(pi) MUL ID(r) RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("area=") RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(put_d) LPAREN ID(pi) MUL ID(r) MUL ID(r) RPAREN SEMICOLON
RBRACE
